author: The Critical Drinker
description: Its been billed as Karate Kid's version of the Avengers, bringing together all the different movies and TV shows, but is it really the epic culmination of a 40 year old story, or just a lame cash grab sequel? Let's find out.
title: Karate Kid Legends - The Weirdest Movie In The Franchise

author: The Critical Drinker
description:
We did it! We made it to the end of Last of Us. Join me, MauLer, Mark Millar, Nerdrotic, Mr H Reviews and Darkhour as we talk about this show's disastrous second season, Superman's rumoured test screenings that prompted major reshoots by James Gunn, Doctor Who's rumoured cancellation when this season ends, and the prospects for the new Harry Potter TV show. Join us for Open Bar 144.

Become a backer for Mark's new comic, Psychic Sam on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sidehustlecomics/psychic-sam-vol-1-of-3

title: Open Bar #144 - Last Of Us Disaster, Superman Test Screenings, Harry Potter Casting
